    "description": "猫猫与罐罐是一款轻松的卡牌迷宫益智游戏，讲述了猫猫寻找它最喜爱的罐罐的故事。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156150/extras/becf8c3c6dc33314001ab8feef676282.poster.avif?t=1727409028\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156150/extras/becf8c3c6dc33314001ab8feef676282.webm?t=1727409028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156150/extras/becf8c3c6dc33314001ab8feef676282.mp4?t=1727409028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156150/extras/1f23f373c5587c42999a59c78ba1f579.poster.avif?t=1727409028\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156150/extras/1f23f373c5587c42999a59c78ba1f579.webm?t=1727409028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156150/extras/1f23f373c5587c42999a59c78ba1f579.mp4?t=1727409028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>利用卡牌和场景上所有的物品帮助猫猫找到它的罐罐!<br><br>猫猫会在不同地方找罐罐，包括草园，森林，沙漠等等地区，不同地区会有不同的动物能够互动!<br><br>在地图上所有物品都是能互动的，包括老虎，树，鸟类，猴子等等...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><br>🐈利用卡牌控制猫咪移动方向<br>🐈与场上物品互动改变猫咪行走路线<br>🐈卡牌阅读方法为由上到下，以这张为例，猫咪会先向上走2格，再向右走2格，最后向下走一格<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156150/extras/萤幕撷取画面_2022-10-24_183724.png?t=1727409028\" /></span><br>🐈游戏目的是让猫咪吃到他最爱的罐罐<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色:</strong></h2><br>🐈<strong>容易控制:</strong><br>🐈🐈你只需要用你的滑鼠就能畅快游玩<br><br>🐈<strong>超多可互动物品:</strong><br>🐈🐈在地图上的物品全都可互动，令到可玩性和难度直线上升，同时你可以看到猫猫可爱的互动情况<br><br>🐈<strong>十分烧脑:</strong><br>🐈🐈别少看这游戏，虽然很可爱但关卡也十分困难，当你成功令猫猫吃到罐罐时会感到满足<br><br>🐈 <strong>丰富的游戏内容:</strong><br>🐈🐈这游戏有高达100关等你来解开<br><br>🐈<strong>全手工制作:</strong><br>🐈🐈每一关都是人手精心设计",
